                                                                                            <p class="p1"><span class="s1"><strong>Admir Skodo</strong> is a Bosnian-Swedish-American writer and historian. He has published essays, reviews, and articles in </span><em><span class="s1">Times Literary Supplement, The Independent,</span></em><span class="s1"> and </span><em><span class="s1">Modern Intellectual History</span></em><span class="s1">, among others. He is completing a collection of stories tentatively entitled </span><em><span class="s1">Comedy and Slaughter.</span></em></p>
